                     <interp inst="t18370403-1082-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18370403-cd-141" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370403-1082-offence-1 t18370403-cd-141"></join>28th of March</rs>, 1 bottle, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370403-name-1022" type="victimName">
